token.tokenizer

Class ATokenizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • token.tokenizer.ATokenizer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITokenizer
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BNFTokenizer, CustomTokenizer, Tokenizer1, XMLTokenizer

    public abstract class ATokenizer
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITokenizer
    Use the StreamTokenizer provided by in java.io to scan an input stream and extract an appropriate Token. Is customizable through the setSymbols() method which takes an Iterable's containing the keywords to recognize as special tokens.
